18 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 11-105.1, is
19 amended to read as follows:
20 Section 11-105.1. A. All curriculum and materials including
21 supplementary materials which will be used to teach or will be used
22 for or in connection with a sex education class or program which is
23 designed for the exclusive purpose of discussing sexual behavior or
24 attitudes, or any test, survey or questionnaire whose primary
